{"tid":83123,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(年青有為)網上留言騷擾女高中生　日醫生被捕","createTime":"2017-01-16T13:21:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-25T07:20:03.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2b595c4c1541e50211c6b74b61fa06f31a74f865","tid":83123,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T13:21:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170116/photo/bknint-20170116174528849-0116_17011_001_01p.jpg?20170116183908\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170116%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20170116174528849-0116_17011_001_01p.jpg%3F20170116183908&h=8d74ee69&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n網上留言即使隱藏身分也要慎言，不然也會觸犯法例。日本一名34歲男醫生，因連續兩個月在同一個女高中生的twitter留下「這是我老婆！」等字眼，遭警方以違反跟蹤犯規制法被捕。 <br />\n<br />\n據報道。石川縣醫生角田真弘在去年10月到12月期間，在心儀的女高中生推文下，留下「這是我老婆！」、「想要掀裙子」、「我知道你的行蹤喔！」以及各種性騷擾字句。 <br />\n<br />\n受害人不堪騷擾報警，角田隨即被警方拘捕並承認罪行，其身份遭「起底」後被網民斥行徑變態可怕。角田化名開設的騷擾用twitter帳號，事後已遭刪除。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170116/photo/bknint-20170116174528849-0116_17011_001_02b.jpg?20170116183908\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170116%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20170116174528849-0116_17011_001_02b.jpg%3F20170116183908&h=398e12e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b0dc41dd5951be656c7ec60dcc97b1ea713bc30","tid":83123,"uid":30578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T13:23:58.000Z","msg":"痴線毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8034b5d3d8a96736bd55581dcebb6ab35c4a106","tid":83123,"uid":15984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T13:24:17.000Z","msg":"女仔Twitter 呢"},{"pid":"0fc75e06d4ce952e5869e8b3bb514c0955aa43b3","tid":83123,"uid":50018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T13:28:35.000Z","msg":"諗起日本維新會單野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"971d89e